{
  "stem": "22944.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't such a big street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used-- yes, we could walk up and down, because matter of, like, the size of this street, [INAUDIBLE] avenue.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't a very large-- could've been bigger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the distance I used to go wasn't very far.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My eldest sister wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She left in 1939 to Palestine, the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that was the last transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I do remember that, with heavy heart, my parents said good bye to my sister who did advise to move, all of us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She belonged to a movement called Maccabi Hatzair, and she went to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were left now, five.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't tell you 100% if it was like that, but I presume that there was already rumors going that people around the age of 17 or 18 were sent to some labor camp to work-- the start of as a teenagers.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or she belonged to the movement who knew something, and recommended, or told, the group to get out if they can-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] or ideological reason.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There may be many reasons why she went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But thank God she did the right move, because she survived the most terrible experience, what we have later on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then, my brother was in a yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was apple of my eye.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I really adored him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had only one brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my other sisters weren't going to school as we always went to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we got on very nicely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had quite a nice relationship, all of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I presume between one or two years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think, in 1941 or '40, all the Jews had to leave Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
